        <h2>Welcome to iRecipe!</h2>
        <p>iRecipe is a platform where you can find, share, and save your favorite recipes. Whether you're a novice cook or an experienced chef, you'll find a variety of recipes to suit your taste and needs.</p>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Our mission is to provide a space where food enthusiasts can discover new dishes, share their own creations, and get inspired by others. We aim to make cooking easier and more enjoyable for everyone.</p>
